bio: Rahul manages Google Developer Group Baroda, and he leads the community. He has representated GDG Baroda at multiple Google Summits, and he has also been at Google I/O 2015 that happened at San Francisco.

bio: Sufficiently qualified to be recognized as a Software Engineer, specialized on mobility and cloud computing platforms(s). I am a part time Gaming Freak and simply crazy for anything with wheels on it.

name: Dhrumil Shah
title: Lead Android Developer
bio: Dhrumil Shah, The Co-Organizer of GDG Ahmedabad, Lead Android Developer at Bugle Technologies Pvt. Ltd. Dhrumil Shah has completed his masters in Computer engineering specialize in Wireless & Mobile Computing. Being a techno freak, his interest lies in developing apps and doing research.

name: Harsh Dattani
title: Technical Speaker
bio: Harsh is a M.Tech Student of Cyber Security from Gujarat Forensic Science University, and he is also Associated with Google Developers Group, Baroda. He focuses more on Android Security. His previous DevFest talk includes “Introduction to Material Design” at DevFest Ahmedabad in December 2014.

name: Anand Thakar

bio: Anand is a Sr. Web Developer at Hidden Brains Infotech. Pvt. Ltd. having 4 years of Experience with the Web Development and holds a Zend php 5.3 Certification.At web front Anand is mainly Active in the Wordpress Community and have been part of Many Wordcamps happen through out the india.During his Free time you can find him either traveling or Watching movies.

name: Darshan Parikh
title: Android Developer
bio: Darshan is an Android Developer at Rigel Networks and a proud member of GDG Baroda. He likes to be in the digital environment of open source technologies where every one can share their work with others. His interest in android development has started in the third year of college. In this time till now he has developed many useful android applications. And still he is a learner.
